summary: House in the lower canal in Riften
descriptionHtml:
A nicer version of one of the houses found in the lower canal in Riften. It has all of your crafting needs covered, as well as a few mannequins, display cases, and weapon racks. It\'s located on the South side of town under the keep - take the stairs outside the orphanage down into the canal and it will be in front of you.

A smaller version of this house can be found at http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/24054/
author: Minkiminks
